    "For example, GPT-2 124M has 124 million parameters, while GPT-3 175B has 175 billion parameters.",
    "These numbers reflect the total count of learnable weights in the neural network.",
    "We implemented text generation using the Huggingface Transformers library 92 with nucleus sampling 93 with a set P value of 0.95 and a temperature value of 1.0.",
